      <title>SBB 债券持有人撤销对房地产集团的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/sbb-bondholder-drops-lawsuit-against-property-group-2025-01-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典银行SBB周一称，其债权人美国对冲基金Fir Tree Partners将终止向该房地产集团追讨剩余750万欧元债券（767万美元）的法律程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/sbb-bondholder-drops-lawsuit-against-property-group-2025-01-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
